  "section_name": "Investment Recommendation & Outlook",
  "text": "Based on the comprehensive analysis of Bank of America's financial performance, competitive positioning, and risk profile, we assign a Hold rating to BAC shares. The company demonstrates solid operational recovery in Q3 2025, with revenue growth accelerating to 3.33% year-over-year and net income rebounding 19.01% from the prior period. However, material risks including elevated leverage, net interest margin compression, and competitive pressures in wealth management warrant a cautious stance rather than an upgrade to Buy.",
